OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFresher conditions spreading to
OL,6,Fall parts, with sunshine and showers
OL,7,Fduring the morning, becoming more
OL,8,Fsettled and drier during the
OL,9,Fafternoon. More seasonable
OL,10,Ftemperatures than expected. Winds
OL,11,Fmoderate southwesterly.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry start to the evening
OL,14,Fbecoming cloudy at times with the
OL,15,Fchance of some isolated showers
OL,16,Fovernight. Feeling cooler overnight
OL,17,Fthan of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
