OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FVariable cloud with some long
OL,6,Fsunny periods developing during the
OL,7,Fday. Clouding over during the evening,
OL,8,Fwith showers overnight some of which
OL,9,Fcould be heavy or even thundery.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FTurning more unsettled on Tuesday with
OL,13,Fsunshine and showers. Wednesday starts
OL,14,Fof sunny, then clouding over with rain
OL,15,Flater. A wet start on Thursday before
OL,16,Fcloud clearing and becoming sunny.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
